---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About - Yonatan N. Degefu">
  <div class="about-container">
    <h1>About Me</h1>

    <section class="bio-section">
      <div class="profile-image">
        <!-- Add your photo here -->
        <div class="placeholder-image">YND</div>
      </div>
      <div class="bio-content">
        <p>
          I am a PhD candidate in Biomedical Engineering at the University of Virginia, working in the
          Fallahi-Sichani Lab. My research focuses on understanding cellular plasticity in melanoma through
          computational and systems biology approaches.
        </p>
        <p>
          I'm passionate about bridging the gap between healthcare and translational research through quantitative
          methods. My work combines mechanistic modeling, single-cell analysis, and drug combination discovery to
          develop more effective cancer therapies.
        </p>
        <p>
          Beyond research, I'm bilingual (English and Amharic), I enjoy the outdoors and love to cook, and am committed
          to community service and scientific outreach. I believe in making science accessible and impactful for
          broader communities.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="education">
      <h2>Education</h2>
      <div class="timeline">
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3>Ph.D. in Biomedical Engineering</h3>
            <p class="institution">University of Virginia, Charlottesville, VA</p>
            <p class="date">August 2021 - Present</p>
            <p class="description">Research: Mechanistic modeling of AP-1 transcriptional dynamics and cellular plasticity in melanoma</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3>B.S. in Biology</h3>
            <p class="institution">Colby-Sawyer College, New London, NH</p>
            <p class="date">September 2014 - May 2018</p>
            <p class="description">Minors: Mathematics & Chemistry | Summa Cum Laude</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="experience">
      <h2>Experience</h2>
      <div class="experience-list">
        <div class="experience-item">
          <h3>Graduate Research Assistant</h3>
          <p class="organization">Fallahi-Sichani Lab, University of Virginia</p>
          <p class="date">November 2021 - Present</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Developed ODE-based mechanistic modeling framework to characterize AP-1 transcriptional factor dynamics</li>
            <li>Built computational pipelines for calibrating models from single-cell multiplexed imaging data</li>
            <li>Integrated Boolean modeling and partial correlation networks to construct de novo regulatory networks</li>
            <li>Mentored summer undergraduate researchers in quantitative biology and data science</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="experience-item">
          <h3>Systems Medicine Intern</h3>
          <p class="organization">AstraZeneca, Gaithersburg, MD</p>
          <p class="date">May 2025 - August 2025</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Designed novel QSP model in MATLAB SimBiology for DNA Damage Response pathways</li>
            <li>Conducted in silico experiments to quantify drug synergy and inform optimal dosing strategies</li>
            <li>Presented findings to stakeholders in Systems Medicine and Clinical Pharmacology</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="experience-item">
          <h3>Research Technician</h3>
          <p class="organization">Aldridge Lab, Tufts University</p>
          <p class="date">June 2018 - May 2021</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Investigated multi-drug combinations against M. tuberculosis using DiaMOND method</li>
            <li>Engineered automated analysis pipeline processing 300,000+ drug combination screens</li>
            <li>Developed predictive models using machine learning to translate in vitro to in vivo outcomes</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: #00ff41;
    text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 255, 65, 0.5);
  }

  h1::before {
    content: '# ';
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin: 3rem 0 1.5rem;
    color: #00ff41;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #00ff41;
  }

  h2::before {
    content: '## ';
  }

  .bio-section {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .placeholder-image {
    width: 200px;
    height: 200px;
    background-color: #0d0d0d;
    border-radius: 4px;
    border: 2px solid #00ff41;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: #00ff41;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .bio-content p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #c0c0c0;
  }

  .timeline {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 2rem;
  }

  .timeline::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 2px;
    background-color: #00ff41;
  }

  .timeline-item {
    position: relative;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .timeline-marker {
    position: absolute;
    left: -2rem;
    top: 0.5rem;
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
    background-color: #00ff41;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 3px solid #1a1a1a;
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 255, 65, 0.5);
  }

  .timeline-content h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: #e0e0e0;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .institution,
  .organization {
    color: #a0a0a0;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .date {
    color: #00ff41;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .description {
    color: #c0c0c0;
    font-style: italic;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .experience-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .experience-item h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: #e0e0e0;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .experience-item ul {
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
    margin-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .experience-item li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: #c0c0c0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .experience-item li::marker {
    color: #00ff41;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .bio-section {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .placeholder-image {
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
